Package solver.analysis.enemyprobability

Class FloodFillPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • solver.analysis.enemyprobability.FloodFillPoint
  • public class FloodFillPoint
extends Object
    Helper class for flood filling the enemy minimum steps by storing a single point which has to be calculated into the minimum steps FloatMatrix.
